data.title: Quarry near Šentrupert, Municipality of Šentrupert Podcast
data.meta_description: Let me tell you about a small corner of Slovenia, Draga pri Šentrupertu. This village is nestled in the northwest of Šentrupert, in the historical region of Lower Carniola, an area that is now included in the southeastern statistical region of Slovenia.
